  "code": "%% L1 to L2 Message Flow\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant User as USER/CONTRACT\n    participant L1 as L1 (LineaRollup)\n    participant Coord as Coordinator\n    participant L2 as L2 (L2MessageService)\n\n    User->>L1: 1. sendMessage()\n    L1->>L1: 2. MessageSent event\n    L1->>Coord: Event detected\n    Coord->>L2: 3. Anchor hash\n    L2->>L2: 4. Hash stored\n    Note over L2: Message now CLAIMABLE\n    User->>L2: 5. claimMessage()<br/>(or Postman)\n    L2->>L2: 6. Execute calldata\n    L2-->>User: Message delivered\n",
  "diagram_type": "participant size:400..600",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T04:03:10.696755",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个从L1到L2的消息跨链流程图。核心参与者有四个：用户或合约、L1上的LineaRollup合约、协调者Coordinator，以及L2的L2MessageService。流程起点是用户在L1调用sendMessage。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "L1",
        "Coordinator",
        "L2",
        "sendMessage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那L1在收到sendMessage之后，是直接把消息发给Coordinator吗？还是说中间有个事件触发的环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "L1",
        "MessageSent",
        "Coordinator"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好问题。L1会先触发一个MessageSent事件，这个事件被Coordinator监听到。所以L1到Coordinator的箭头应该标注\"Event detected\"，表示协调者在监听链上事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "L1",
        "MessageSent",
        "Coordinator",
        "Event detected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础结构画出来：四个参与者纵向排列，User到L1的sendMessage调用，L1内部的MessageSent事件，以及L1到Coordinator的事件检测。接下来Coordinator到L2的动作是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "L1",
        "Coordinator",
        "sendMessage",
        "MessageSent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Coordinator检测到事件后，会向L2发送一个anchor hash，也就是把L1的状态根锚定到L2上。L2收到后会把hash存下来，这时候消息状态就变成\"CLAIMABLE\"了。我需要在L2上方加一个注释框说明这个状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Coordinator",
        "L2",
        "anchor hash",
        "Hash stored",
        "CLAIMABLE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Coordinator到L2是\"Anchor hash\"，L2内部是\"Hash stored\"，然后在L2上方加Note标注\"Message now CLAIMABLE\"。之后用户就可以在L2上claim消息了，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Coordinator",
        "L2",
        "anchor hash",
        "CLAIMABLE",
        "claimMessage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，用户调用claimMessage，这里也可以由Postman代执行。然后L2内部执行calldata，最后把消息投递给用户。注意最后一步用虚线箭头，表示这是返回或回调，不是新的调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "L2",
        "claimMessage",
        "Postman",
        "Execute calldata",
        "Message delivered"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程：User→L1发送消息，L1触发事件，Coordinator监听并锚定hash到L2，L2存储后消息可领取，User或Postman在L2 claim并执行，最终消息投递完成。需要调整什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "L1",
        "Coordinator",
        "L2",
        "sendMessage",
        "MessageSent",
        "anchor hash",
        "CLAIMABLE",
        "claimMessage",
        "Execute calldata",
        "Message delivered"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个流程准确反映了L1到L2的跨链消息机制。标注也清晰，可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "L1",
        "Coordinator",
        "L2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
